Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.44,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:42.93,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}爱上他人 又无法入眠
